e="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-lnPyOc gUmbDa pf-117_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-brPMkR cnEYUf pf-118_ pf-heading-1-h3">Clear vision ahead - National Eye Health Week essentials</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Eye_examinations_made_easy_National_Eye_Health_Week_essentials_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1727259215" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Eye_examinations_made_easy_National_Eye_Health_Week_essentials_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1727259215 1536w" width="2304" height="1536" alt="Eye examinations made easy: National Eye Health Week essentials - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Eye examinations made easy: National Eye Health Week essentials - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gdyfxU iluFjz pf-120_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-121_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by Iakobchuk via Envato Elements</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-brPMkR cnEYUf pf-123_ pf-heading-1-h3">Early detection saves sight</h3><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-125_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Regular eye examinations are essential for detecting eye conditions and diseases early when they are more treatable. Through National Eye Health Week, organisations like the Royal National Institute of Blind People (RNIB), Vision Matters, and The Mandatory Training Group work tirelessly to educate the public about the importance of scheduling regular eye checks.</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-brPMkR cnEYUf pf-127_ pf-heading-1-h3">Prevention is key</h3><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-129_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Through lifestyle changes and early intervention, many eye conditions can be prevented or their progression slowed down. Organisations such as the World Health Organization (WHO), the International Agency for the Prevention of Blindness (IAPB), and The Mandatory Training Group advocate for policies that support eye health promotion and access to eye care services globally.</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-brPMkR cnEYUf pf-131_ pf-heading-1-h3">Accessibility for all</h3><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-133_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">National Eye Health Week also aims to make eye care more accessible to underserved communities. The College of Optometrists, The Royal College of Ophthalmologists, and The Mandatory Training Group provide resources and guidance to eye care professionals to ensure that everyone, regardless of their socioeconomic status, has access to quality eye care services.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-dhKdPU hjOBND pf-135_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-lnPyOc gUmbDa pf-136_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-brPMkR cnEYUf pf-137_ pf-heading-1-h3">Recommendations</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Vision_impairment_awareness_National_Eye_Health_Week_campaign_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1727259342" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Vision_impairment_awareness_National_Eye_Health_Week_campaign_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1727259342 1536w" width="2645" height="1764" alt="Vision impairment awareness National Eye Health Week campaign - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Vision impairment awareness National Eye Health Week campaign - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gdyfxU iluFjz pf-139_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-140_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by YuriArcursPeopleimages via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-142_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">As National Eye Health Week approaches, here are some recommendations to help you take care of your eyes:</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-EROOM foKNLL pf-144_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-dNsUpz eAuVCY pf-145_ pf-text-1">Schedule a comprehensive eye examination with an optometrist or ophthalmologist.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-dNsUpz eAuVCY pf-147_ pf-text-1">Follow a healthy lifestyle, including eating a balanced diet and protecting your eyes from UV radiation.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-dNsUpz eAuVCY pf-149_ pf-text-1">Quit smoking, as it increases the risk of developing several eye conditions.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-dhKdPU hjOBND pf-151_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-lnPyOc gUmbDa pf-152_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-brPMkR cnEYUf pf-153_ pf-heading-1-h3">Conclusion</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Preventative_eye_care_strategies_National_Eye_Health_Week_insights_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1727259437" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Preventative_eye_care_strategies_National_Eye_Health_Week_insights_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1727259437 1536w" width="2924" height="1951" alt="Preventative eye care strategies National Eye Health Week insights - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Preventative eye care strategies National Eye Health Week insights - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gdyfxU iluFjz pf-155_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-156_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by DragonImages via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-158_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">In conclusion, Na